<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idc9d28167-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Another <ref href="/us/pl/102/575/s1636">section 1636 of Pub. L. 102–575</ref> was renumbered 1637 and is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t43/s390h–19">section 390h–19 of this title</ref>.</p>
